description: With his parents away, Greyson Lane wants to play. All he needs now is a partner in crime, and luckily, bestie Theo Brady is always down for a party, especially if it's a private party for two. That's just what Greyson has in mind, so Theo wastes no time heading over. Theo has been waiting for quite some time to be alone with Greyson like this: uninhibited, without worry of being caught, and now that he's got Greyson all to himself, he takes full advantage of the lack of adult supervision, having his way with Greyson as the two of them get into all sorts of unsupervised fun. And this party won't stop until both of them have popped!Enjoy!
title: Unsupervised
